data.description: Main floor living with no steps inside or outside! Twin homes with zero entry rarely come on the market, so here's your chance! 2BR/1BA/1Car attached garage. 972 sqft. The front entry has a double closet to store coats, boots, vacuum and more! The living room provides many options for furniture arrangements. The informal dining room has a door to the laundry/utility room (washer/dryer included), then the attached garage. The wide galley kitchen has newer matching black appliances (included). Circle around to the hallway which takes you to the 2 bedrooms and full bathroom. The bedrooms are next to each other and have double closets.  The full bathroom has a linen closet and large vanity with storage. Notice the grab bars already installed. If you crave outside living, you will love the large enclosed porch. There is a patio for grilling as well. Carpets have been professionally cleaned and fresh paint throughout. All ductwork has also been cleaned. Grab this one quick before it's gone!
